></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n男仔追女仔成日都諗唔到點樣開始個話題嘅<br />\n<br />\n驚太過唐突會令到對方反感<br />\n<br />\n我嘅提議：可以喺同成班人出去玩嘅時候，試下多啲同佢接觸，傾下唔同野，如果個女仔好靜嘅話，你唔洗expect佢會主動同你傾計，所以你更加要主動咁去發現自己，傾下有關佢嘅興趣，當你地開始熟，咁就可以去第二個步驟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望巴打可以同佢熟啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果無共同朋友可以點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4dacd55db10c7275f9ed158172200c425feac1d","tid":459150,"uid":11548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d34822ca96665fd64451eb1ebb3de62e47573bd","tid":459150,"uid":11548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c3606b4267027dfbdaf13ef6655dfc05d0aa72","tid":459150,"uid":8091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:38:02.000Z","msg":"唉 好灰"},{"pid":"1fcfef58b8cf79215f8b74a3658eeec978c861bf","tid":459150,"uid":70135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b396d4cd1fd2a04ee04b68fce5c061649abfbd9f","tid":459150,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T18:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f35d02820d753670ed18f5dc1c9702fe8e9f58c","tid":459150,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T18:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647e0aab0a77ae8941e80c26f98ddf3409aa49ff","tid":459150,"uid":154025,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"